CatDescriptText: Cutline for image (or 2001.35.44342) published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 15, 1955, pg. 6, reads: "Nied Aluminum Products - This is the new location of Nied Aluminum Products, Inc., at 2832 Saw Mill Run Boulevard.  The firm has been in the home improvement business for twenty years.  The public is invited to visit their new showroom displaying aluminum doors, windows, screens and aluminum siding. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Automobiles parked in front of Nied Aluminum Products with advertisement for Shieldall, 2832 Saw Mill Run Boulevard
